{"tid":1112203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 團結香港基金：公屋平均輪候時間將突破6年","createTime":"2019-04-17T09:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T10:28:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e736418a408c93d834cf27c2e586774248e281","tid":1112203,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"團結香港基金發表新一期土地及房屋政策倡議報告，表示公屋平均輪候時間將突破6年，2023年的私人住宅供應量會較去年跌4成。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，政府在最新的《長遠房屋策略》周年進度報告，宣布將新落成的公私營房屋單位的供應比例，由六四比改為七三比，令私人住宅的單位供應目標，由年均的18000個降至13500個。報告又指出，去年上蓋工程動工量明顯下降，可建私人住宅的熟地供應亦大幅減少，令私人住宅單位的落成量大幅減少。<br />\n<br />\n基金建議當局，加速發展25幅土地改劃，同時考慮西貢十四鄉兩幅合共64公頃的山坡地，提供約2至3萬個住宅單位，以及盡快開展110公頃棕地及150公頃私人新界農地的改劃工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453344-20190417.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453344-20190417.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d13a0d7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453344-20190417.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3912d7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453344-20190417.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bbea3c1bca1c873f6a0fae77fbb4f7e325e3f168","tid":1112203,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55104ae9193478d5de3da06d3cff3f28ead7545","tid":1112203,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"990d4c8e8721aacf3d52927d60fb8fbf19085426","tid":1112203,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}